423 ·​·​·​·​·​*·​·​if·​the·​aircraft·​yaw·​changes,​·​the·​camera·​will·​continue·​pointing·​in·​the·​same·​
424 ·​·​·​·​·​*·​·​world·​direction.​·​This·​feature·​is·​supported·​by·​the·​X3,​·​X5·​and·​X5R·​camera·​

429 ·​·​·​·​/​**

431 ·​·​·​·​·​*·​·​follow·​the·​aircraft's·​heading,​·​and·​the·​gimbal·​roll·​will·​follow·​the·​RC's

439 ·​·​·​·​·​*·​·​the·​gimbal·​yaw·​will·​be·​fixed,​·​while·​pitch·​and·​roll·​will·​be·​available·​to·​move.​
